'''Robin Gerardus Petrus Roefs''' (born 17 January 2003) is a Dutch professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[goalkeeper (association football)|goalkeeper]] for {{English football updater|Sunderld}} club [[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]] and the [[Netherlands national football team|Netherlands national team]].

==Club career==
===NEC===
Roefs started off in the youth squads of [[VV Heeswijk]] until he got scouted by [[NEC Nijmegen|NEC]] in 2014.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=VV Heeswijk|url=https://www.vvheeswijk.nl/club-info/nieuwsarchief/499-heeswijks-talent-in-gesprek-met-robin-roefs|title=Heeswijks talent! In gesprek met: Robin Roefs|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl|archive-date=26 May 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240526143825/https://www.vvheeswijk.nl/club-info/nieuwsarchief/499-heeswijks-talent-in-gesprek-met-robin-roefs|url-status=dead}}</ref> In the 2021–22 season he was training goalkeepers for [[VV Heeswijk]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=DVV Heeswijk|url=https://www.vvheeswijk.nl/club-info/nieuwsarchief/1111-nieuwe-doelen-dankzij-robin-roefs|title=Nieuwe doelen dankzij Robin Roefs|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl|archive-date=26 May 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240526143824/https://www.vvheeswijk.nl/club-info/nieuwsarchief/1111-nieuwe-doelen-dankzij-robin-roefs|url-status=dead}}</ref>

Roefs extended his contract at NEC until 2028 in September 2023.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Gelderlander|url=https://www.gelderlander.nl/nec/nec-bindt-toekomstig-eerste-doelman-roefs-langer-aan-zich-jeugdproduct-tekent-bij-tot-2028~a9dfbd99/|title=NEC bindt 'toekomstig eerste doelman' Roefs langer aan zich: jeugdproduct tekent bij tot 2028|date= 5 September 2023|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl}}</ref> Later that same month Roefs made his professional debut in a 3–0 victory against [[FC Utrecht|Utrecht]] in the [[Eredivisie]], coming on as a substitute for the injured [[Jasper Cillessen]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=DTV Nieuws|url=https://dtvnieuws.nl/nieuws/artikel/robin-roefs-maakt-eredivisie-debuut-voor-nec|title=Robin Roefs maakt Eredivisie-debuut voor NEC|date= 23 September 2023|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl}}</ref> The week after his debut, he made his first start for NEC in a 3–1 loss against [[SBV Vitesse|Vitesse]].<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Gelderlander|url=https://www.gelderlander.nl/nec/vitesse-deelt-mokerslag-uit-aan-nec-duel-tijdelijk-gestaakt-gooiers-plastic-bekers-gepakt~a608c496/#:~:text=Vitesse%20heeft%20de%20Gelderse%20derby,op%20het%20veld%20werden%20gegooid|title=Vitesse deelt mokerslag uit aan NEC: duel tijdelijk gestaakt, 'gooiers plastic bekers gepakt'|date= 1 October 2023|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl}}</ref> In May 2024, Roefs hinted at a possible exit as he wanted more playtime.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=De Brug Nijmegen|url=https://www.brugnijmegen.nl/nieuws/algemeen/180787/nec-keeper-roefs-ik-wil-spelen-anders-gaan-we-verder-kijken|title=NEC-keeper Roefs: 'Ik wil spelen, anders gaan we verder kijken'|date=8 May 2024|access-date=26 May 2024|language=nl}}</ref>

===Sunderland===
On 1 August 2025, newly promoted [[Premier League]] club [[Sunderland A.F.C.|Sunderland]] announced the signing of Roefs on a five-year contract.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.safc.com/news/2025/august/01/robin-roefs-seals-sunderland-move/ |title=ROBIN ROEFS SEALS SUNDERLAND MOVE |publisher=Sunderland A.F.C. |date=1 August 2025 |access-date=1 August 2025}}</ref>

He made his debut for Sunderland in their opening match of the [[2025–26 Premier League]] season, keeping a clean sheet in a 3–0 win over [[West Ham United F.C.|West Ham United]] on 16 August.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.safc.com/news/2025/august/16/Record--It-was-a-day-for-the-Sunderland-debutants/|title=Record: It was a day for the Sunderland debutants|date=17 August 2025|access-date=8 March 2026|website=Sunderland A.F.C.}}</ref>

On 10 January 2026, Roefs saved all three of [[Everton F.C.|Everton]]'s kicks in a 3–0 [[penalty shootout]] win for Sunderland in the third round of the [[2025–26 FA Cup|FA Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11095/13492562/everton-1-1-sunderland-aet-0-3-on-pens-robin-roefs-saves-every-penalty-in-shootout-to-steer-black-cats-through|title=Everton 1-1 Sunderland AET (0-3 on pens): Robin Roefs saves every penalty in shoot-out to send Black Cats through|date=10 January 2026|access-date=8 March 2026|website=Sky Sports}}</ref>

==International career==
On 29 August 2025, Roefs received his first call-up to the senior [[Netherlands national football team|Netherlands]] squad. On 3rd June 2026, he made his debut against [[Algeria national football team|Algeria]] in [[Rotterdam]], replacing [[Bart Verbruggen]] at half-time. In the 86th minute, he conceded a volley shot from [[Anis Hadj Moussa]], as the home side suffered a surprise 0–1 loss.<ref>{{cite web |title=Koeman announces Oranje national team call-ups: Two debutants present |url=https://onefootball.com/en/news/koeman-announces-oranje-national-team-call-ups-two-debutants-present-41583257 |website=[[OneFootball]] |access-date=31 August 2025 |date=29 August 2025}}</ref>

